---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Sơn Lê">
  <Nav active="about" />

  <div class="page-wrap">
    <h1 class="page-title">Sơn Lê</h1>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2 class="about-h2">VC, then operator, now builder</h2>
      <p>
        I started out writing checks. I sat across the table from founders, evaluated
        bets, and learned what makes a company work and what quietly sinks one.
      </p>
      <p>
        Then I crossed over and ran things instead of judging them. Years as an operator
        taught me that building is harder than betting, and a lot more honest about whether
        you were right.
      </p>
      <p>
        Now I build my own. From Saigon, mostly solo, shipping real products and writing
        about what I learn doing it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2 class="about-h2">What I'm doing now</h2>
      <p>
        I'm the founder of <a href="https://perfeat.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="accent-link">Perfeat ↗</a>,
        a private food diary where every meal gets a rating and a page. It started as a way
        to remember the meals worth remembering, and turned into the thing I work on most days.
      </p>
      <p>
        I build with a lot of AI tooling, and I lean on it heavily. It does not replace the
        decisions, the taste, or the judgment about what is actually worth making. That part
        is still the job.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2 class="about-h2">Why I write</h2>
      <p>
        Writing is how I figure out what I actually think. I keep notes on the years as they
        happen, on specific things I have lived through, and on how people decide and change
        their minds. Some of it will end up here.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am not trying to teach anyone. I am trying to be honest about what building is like
        while I am still in the middle of it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-cta">
      <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">See what I'm building</a>
      <a href="/writing" class="btn-ghost">Read the writing</a>
    </div>

    <div class="about-contact">
      <div class="about-contact-label">Find me elsewhere</div>
      <div class="about-socials">
        <a href="mailto:tuanson.le03@gmail.com" class="about-social accent">tuanson.le03@gmail.com ↗</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/sonlndv" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-social accent">X / Twitter ↗</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/toilaleson" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-social accent">GitHub ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
